The use of a simulator to guide the optimization process suggests an artificial intelligence (cs.AI) component to the work. Additionally, the use of a machine learning accelerator (Cambricon-1A ISA) suggests a potential overlap with neural engineering (cs.NE) or robotics (cs.AR) research.
